data.description: This Ranch home offers luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout. Water heater and dishwasher new in 2020.  Cove ceilings in living room.  Ready for buyer to come in and make it their own.  Close to gas station, cleaners, grocery store, coffee shops, and more... Within 10 miles there are 4 parks and over 70 restaurants for you to explore. Home is vacant and easy to show. Offers a large, fenced back yard. Furnace inspection completed and City inspection required for C of O will be completed by Seller prior to closing.  Home being sold AS-IS. Any additional costs/repairs if Buyer obtaining FHA financing will be Buyer's responsibility.
